  <div class="row text-medium">
    <b> Details </b><br>
    4 full days over 2 weekends in the late autumn
    <ul>
        <li>Weekend 1: Fundamentals of Skiing - November 17th & 18th, 9am - 4pm</li>
        <li>Weekend 2: Fundamentals of Teaching - December 1st & 2nd, 9am - 4pm</li>
        <ul>
          <li>* Includes a final written exam *</li>
